What Is Business Communication ?

* Effective Business Communication Skills: Agar ap ksi business se related ksi business ke fard se baat krke apna koi goal/discussion achieve krne ki koshish krhay toh woh business communication mein aagaya.

Types Of Communication:

* Verbal Communication: Kay Apse zubaani baat krna
* Non-Verbal Communication: Kay ap eye contact,facial expression ke saath msg dena.
* Written Communication: Kay likh ke communicate krna.
* Visual Communication: Koi cheez dikha kr communicate krna like photso and videos etc.
* Listen Communication:  Most Important ,seekhne ki garz se sunna listen communication kehlati hai ,na kay jawab dene ke garz se sunain.